### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمْ قَالُوا۟ لَن تَمَسَّنَا ٱلنَّارُ إِلَّآ أَيَّامًا مَّعْدُودَٰتٍ ۖ وَغَرَّهُمْ فِى دِينِهِم مَّا كَانُوا۟ يَفْتَرُونَ</span>

### English

This is because they say, “The Fire will not touch us except for a few days.” They have been deceived in their faith by their wishful lying.